snippet.title: The Real Reason Why Artie Lange Hates Howard Stern
snippet.description:
Howard Stern is a far less controversial figure than he was during his shock jock days, but that doesn’t mean he’s devoid of enemies. Just ask Artie Lange, who was once a sidekick on The Howard Stern Show, but left the popular radio show in 2009 due to his drug problem and never returned. He’s spoken out against Stern in the years since, and while some fans may hope for a reunion between the two, it doesn’t seem likely that they’ll be working together again any time soon. Let’s take a look at the real reasons why Artie Lange hates Howard Stern.
